<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Profile - Nutrition App</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/navbar.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/profile.css">
</head>

<body>
    {{>navbar user=user}}

    <div class="profile-container">
        <div class="user-info">
            <h2>Welcome, {{user.username}} 👋</h2>
            <p>This is your personalized nutrition dashboard.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>🧪 Search by Nutrient</h3>
            <p>Input a nutrient and amount (e.g., <strong>protein 10</strong>) to find foods with:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>✅ Nutrient less than your input</li>
                <li>🚀 Nutrient greater than your input</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/search">Explore by Nutrient</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>🔍 Search by Food Name</h3>
            <p>Type a food item like <strong>"Apple"</strong> to get its nutrition info including protein, fat, sugar, etc.</p>
            <a href="/searchName">Go to Search</a>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">
            <h3>📅 Daily Nutrition Tracker</h3>
            <p>Enter foods you’ve eaten today and get your total intake of proteins, fats, sugar, and carbs.</p>
            <a href="/findTotal">Track Today's Nutrition</a>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>
